---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="About Consumer Product Recalls and its maker, Adrian Nesta.">
  <div class="max-w-prose">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold sm:text-4xl">About</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-muted">
      Hi, I'm Adrian Nesta, a data engineer and journalist. I have a passion for making publicly
      available data more accessible and useful, and this site is one of those efforts. It pulls
      together U.S. consumer product recalls from five federal agencies into one place you can
      actually search, browse and query.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-muted">
      You can find more about me and my other work at
      <a href="https://justanesta.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">justanesta.com</a
      >. If the site is useful to you and you'd like to support it, you can
      <a href="https://www.buymeacoffee.com/justanesta" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >buy me a coffee</a
      >.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-muted">
      Feedback and ideas for improving the site or the data behind it are always welcome.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>
